  <project_license>MIT</project_license>

  <name>Quran Radio</name>
  <summary>Stream Quran Karim radio stations from your system tray</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Quran Radio is a lightweight system tray application for Linux that lets
      you listen to Quran Karim radio stations without opening a browser or a
      heavy media player.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Two built-in stations: Quran Kareem Beirut and Cairo (ERTU 98.2 FM)</li>
      <li>Play, stop, and switch stations directly from the tray menu</li>
      <li>Volume slider in the controls popup</li>
      <li>Remembers your last station and volume across sessions</li>
      <li>Minimal, dark-themed interface with Islamic green accents</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.AhmadTakkoush">
